Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 years have passed since the \NWar of the Best in Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew returned\N to Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they reached the Fish-Man Island \Nlocated 10,000 meters below sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to invite you to \Nthe Ryugu Palace-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:42.20,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Ryugu Palace! Taken by \Nthe Shark that They Saved!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:04:00.05,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A FEW HOURS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few hours before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Luffy and the others met King Neptune...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:04.01,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,700)}THE RYUGU KINGDOM MERMAID COVE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Mermaid Cove in the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody sealed this very tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I wonder what's inside.\N--Let me guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the barrel is so important to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like a treasure chest, it must be \Nhigh-quality liquor or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You loosened it up pretty \Nwell and that's enough for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? There's someone inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your help, Mermaids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the water now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a swamp! On rocky ground?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a muddy swamp that you can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bottomless swamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Devil Fruit eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the Swamp-Swamp Fruit \Nand became a swamp man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...The more you sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling for help! \NI'm not gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Stop," didn't I? You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to sleep for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is bottomless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now how much were Mermaids going for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, \N70 million each at auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got 3 of them so that'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to thank the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of them, I made it \Ninto the Fish-Man Island
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without going through immigration!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hunt these valuable \NMermaids as much as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a treasure island for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I heard them around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishilly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.33,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,AT THE PRESENT TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at Coral Hill, the port \Ntown in the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:19.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,700)}THE RYUGU KINGDOM\NTHE PORT TOWN--CORAL HILL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They kidnapped girls from the Mermaid Cove?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant.\N They were all pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, they're Camie's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they made a threat against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, at the place at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthere were only us guards, the Mermaid girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the guys from the Fish-Man \NDistrict who were beaten,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now they're gone so who \Nknows what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans have a good reason\N to kidnap Mermaids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Mermaid girls have been \Ntraded at high prices in their world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't suspect them blindly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know that there \Nwere a lot of pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who got close to Mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...pretending they were \Nnice only to kidnap them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Madam Sharley, did you really see the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N future that you mentioned a while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the pirate - Straw Hat Luffy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwill destroy the Fish-Man Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Sharley, drink some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I saw the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the people at the Ryugu Palace like us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,know how accurate your previsions are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:09:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to treat them nicely \Nsince they saved my sister's pet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although everything remains uncertain,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't let them be at large!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to \Ntake them into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.94,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,AROUND THE SAME TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:15.40,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,700)}THE RYUGU KINGDOM\NTHE HIGH-CLASS DISTRICT--FISHVERLY HILLS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the high-class district\N of the Ryugu Kingdom -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishverly Hills...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who were they after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune came to pick them up himself\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and invited them to the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark! Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jamon! Jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jamon! Jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jamon! Jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that chant, old \Nman? It sounds so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's rude! Straw, you bastard! \NTerrifying! You're terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shark--Megalo is a pet that \Nmy daughter loves so much-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She kept crying hysterically \Nsaying "Megalo is not coming back."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aware he was attacked by the Kraken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N Thank you for saving him from danger-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't mean to but I'm\N glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the Mermaid Princess' pet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pappagu-san? If I'm correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you said you're the best friend \Nof the Mermaid Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that was a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I feel sorry for Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to see the Mermaid \NPrincess more than anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he was just born to be unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a princess who has a \Nshark as a pet must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for us to go to the Ryugu Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "Your friends can \Ncome-jamon" so it should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you're not allowed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N Then, why don't you just enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent out my sons first but\N they haven't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can't wait to see the food at the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbanquet so I want to start already-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two, quit drooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I almost forget. I already \Ninvited one of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He started drinking on his \Nown before the banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun to have a banquet \Nwith everybody - he is so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think his name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soldiers will find the rest of your \Nfriends and bring them to the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't worry-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, don't you know where they went?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a good place to shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it won't take that much \Nto get some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Luffy and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I wanna know \Nthe most is the whereabouts of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my shipwright master - \NTom-san's relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where he came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If his family is here, I have \Nto tell them the way he lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got back together \Nbut let me do this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like \Nthere is any stopping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna check on something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of ancient \Ntraditions on the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there must be some \Nimportant pieces of history
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that haven't been revealed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Important pieces of history...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we got separated again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have any problem either, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Well, there was a little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, by the way, grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call him "God of the Sea - Neptune-sama"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is at 10,000 \Nmeters below sea level
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N so why is there light around this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island itself doesn't\N provide any light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only place in the deep sea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that has light so Fish-Men started\N living here a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was the beginning\N of the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are the roots of a giant \Ntree called the Sun Tree Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that transfers sunlight from\N the surface to the deep sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transfers sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there is a tree with
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shining roots more than 10,000 meters long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scientists try to make some senses out of it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a mystical tree that transfers\N sunlight to its roots-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And its respiration supplies\N air to the sea floor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the boss of the Hustle\N Muscle Mangrove at Sabaody?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hairy old man, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the entrance-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes?\N--It's me-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It must be K-King-sama!\N I'll put down the gateway now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Bubbly Coral.\NYou can make a bubble easily with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the palace is filled with sea water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need a good bubble-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't wait to see the Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should we do, Pappagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a man who was invited to the Ryugu Palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become even more famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is twitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.02,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}THE ROYAL PALACE OF THE RYUGU KINGDOM\NTHE RYUGU PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pappagu-san's house is \Nnothing compared to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--King Neptune is back!\N--We were wondering where you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gate will open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This palace looks fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my palace-jamon!\N Stay as long as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, you did it again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must learn your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went out of the palace on your own again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's inexcusable to go down to \Nthe lower world without guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't happen again-jamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got yelled at...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be too late once something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know the situation\N of this country right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have the banquet already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I brought the people who \Nsaved Megalo when he got attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the Kraken-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now welcome our guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the Princess?\NWhat is Princess Shirahoshi doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, King-sama, \Nit happened again a few minutes ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You have to guard the \NPrincess to keep her calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go missing when something\N like that is happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't you see that it'd make everyone in \Nthe palace worry, King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really won't happen again-jamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got yelled at again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:03.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm very sorry that you just brought
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:07.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}THE RYUGU KINGDOM\NTHE MINISTER OF THE RIGHT (SEAHORSE MERMAN)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:07.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the guests here personally \Nbut there's a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:12.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Prince Fukaboshi just called in and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:13.59,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}THE RYUGU KINGDOM\NTHE MINISTER OF THE LEFT (CATFISH MERMAN)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.29,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi did? What was it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they gonna entertain us yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where did Luffy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was here a couple minutes ago. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool can't stay still even for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't just wander around \Nthe holy palace of the Sea God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no mistake! I can smell\N food in the sea water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smells really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no water here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be through those doors then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is a banquet room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said Zoro is here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What huge, thick, solid-looking doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These walls look very solid too.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like the ones in Impel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have really good food inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dark. This isn't a banquet room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was delicious food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is this food storage?\N Who cares! I'll have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Such a funny feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coral is everywhere on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? It's so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did I hear someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This coral is like pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is somebody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing on my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It was a big \Nperson... I mean, Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to kill me \Nlike the others, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am Neptune's daughter!\NSo I'm not scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Not scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody! Father-sama! Brother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa! I didn't do \Nanything to you, did I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, damn! What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi is a gigantic mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken has doggedly pursued her, so she has lived for years in the Hard Shell Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decken hurls an axe at the tower in an attempt to take Shirahoshi's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Nami's group has been surrounded by soldiers from Neputune's army!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Coward and a Crybaby! \NThe Princess in the Hard Shell Tower!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
